  "id": "RAW_b3e70598",
  "title": "1100 多个模型殊途同归，指向一个「通用子空间」，柏拉图又赢一回？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651007176&idx=2&sn=a68a3f775ff535b6aae480ff40a4b270",
  "date": "2025-12-14 04:50:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
